@flotus @drbiden stars on the cover of our August issue!

“During the campaign, I felt so much anxiety from people; they were scared,” @drbiden reflects. “When I travel around the country now, I feel as though people can breathe again.”

Tap the link in our bio to read why @drbiden is the hardworking, heart-on-her-sleeve, everywhere-at-once @flotus that America needs now. Photographed by @annieleibovitz, styled by @tonnegood, written by @jonathanvanmeter, Vogue, August 2021
